title: Gary Bartz & Jon Batiste talking about Jazz, Beethoven & Jimmy Reed backstage Rockwood Music Hall  M

http_headers.User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/71.0.3578.126 Safari/537.36

description:
On their one night off form a tour that's been going on since last October, Jon Batiste And Stay Human booked two last minute sets at Rockwood Music Hall to benefit the National Jazz Museum in Harlem . And as a special surprise, the legendary saxophone player, Gary Bartz sat in both sets. I was lucky to catch an intimate conversation between Gary & Jon on composing. Here's the second half in which they got from Jazz, to Classical to Blues in under 5 minutes!

Shot on the Nikon D4
